{"tid":1538644,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［召喚攬炒］係時候黎多次全球登報","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:39:00.000Z","uid":199669,"like":103,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d6b43409009285a9fc358a62f685128cfc3084","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E7%BC%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%2F&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq6QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=13db90f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%2F&h=77463261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95-%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E7%BC%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n話比全球聽，場杖未完，因為惡法陸續有黎，清算已經開始。<br />\n話比美國聽，we want fire，推動人權法，停止關系法。唔好再信中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2551dfad6d7be83db60a9fc5843f0f71e26013","tid":1538644,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:08.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ad9c3430cb257446f983224f2204da0ce64533","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"大家上twitter講住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #standwithhk"},{"pid":"265c40a43f02fdb6973f2448ba8154d9b7aa660b","tid":1538644,"uid":152815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"若我們接受了政府的條件<br />\n我們已死去的朋友<br />\n是不會原諒我們的<br />\n<br />\n勿忘初衷 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"c663a29f7fcece817bf809b52abf38dff29c280e","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"記住光復香港 時代革命<br />\n我地唔係跪地要中國比民主<br />\n而係要求中國守諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c833eb89d0b05c29de650ee7acbc769d0bed0fc","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"一條小小既法已經令我地血流不止<br />\n仲有無數既法埋緊身"},{"pid":"cfee8a5ee8d386eed1efec5b75c06358b712a1c7","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"貿易戰 係我地最後既舞台，美國唔係聖人，過左貿易戰就無人會再幫我地出聲"},{"pid":"b57ee46f1ae9476c4ee9667da1d8155cb215fd4e","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記初衷 14年既初衷 雙真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a04a985153a9151372f22799919933dfdbdac60","tid":1538644,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"ec08d9ac71b3abb048b0771f47091a62850296ed","tid":1538644,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xcgb58P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxcgb58P.gif&h=4c045c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep8qq8P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp8qq8P.gif&h=b74f62eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div>"},{"pid":"4504841efd4590c588ef1fe2fb273d6e2e9de303","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a04a985153a9151372f22799919933dfdbdac60","tid":1538644,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"有無效唔知 不過值得做 但係只著黑衫係無撚用嫁"},{"pid":"f15f5a8c5dee7fc8f07cb71fe86bd11df187e6cb","tid":1538644,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4504841efd4590c588ef1fe2fb273d6e2e9de303","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a04a985153a9151372f22799919933dfdbdac60","tid":1538644,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:12.000Z","msg":"有無效唔知 不過值得做 但係只著黑衫係無撚用嫁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"俾連黑衫都未開始著嘅人一個機會 做多半步<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c641ff40e314f4b7796d88e5f4a8f7070a8f911","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:47:29.000Z","msg":"由一開始 我地就知道 反送中只係引子 核心從來都係 一次又一次既dq 無數既惡法 國歌法 國民教育法 蒙面法<br />\n只要我地一放鬆 就會開始清算 面臨數以十年的監禁<br />\n係fb ig 出過聲，出黎去過和理非既人祝你間公司唔係紅底，因為你份工好快會比中國人取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5966e6fa1cea2f8c658458386f99fbefb15739e","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"監控燈塔已經陸續起緊，遊行既成本只會愈黎愈高。<br />\n而下一次唔會再有人願意企出黎<br />\n因為再一次被出賣"},{"pid":"d95ad1ec382244bd99637466a435704dfd74e49a","tid":1538644,"uid":199669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"屌推post真係好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb6532aca9a171be2aa2ca876c6fb799297f020","tid":1538644,"uid":295304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ff8829473891c3c861b2039e174ee64dce21f9e4","tid":1538644,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"推，我都覺得要有新一輪文宣方向<br />\n<br />\n要解釋721 831，仲有好多好多令香港人瞓唔著覺既夜晚發生左咩事，所以港人先希望攞到真普選，真正掌握自己既命運<br />\n<br />\n尤其對外國人，始終外國人唔係香港，冇經歷過呢啲令人痛心疾首既黑夜，我擔心唔講清楚會開始有人覺得我地之前暫緩唔收貨，依家連撤回都唔收貨，得寸進尺<br />\n<br />\n要大大聲話比佢地知: 經歷過呢啲事之後，我地一早已經講<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e71338e5839d6ad69232d448bc6dcb54588ad3","tid":1538644,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi